		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Bug: The first frame that each background is scrolled incorrectly.
<br />Possible cause: You are turning on rendering during draw time.
<br />If so, here's a fix: Wait until vblank time to turn on rendering.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


